{"tha-ap537:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap537:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap537:0.3":"Kumarakassapattheraapadana ","tha-ap537:1.1":"“Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap537:1.2":"kappe uppajji nayako; ","tha-ap537:1.3":"Sabbalokahito viro, ","tha-ap537:1.4":"padumuttaranamako. ","tha-ap537:2.1":"Tadaham brahmano hutva, ","tha-ap537:2.2":"vissuto vedaparagu; ","tha-ap537:2.3":"Divaviharam vicaram, ","tha-ap537:2.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap537:3.1":"Catusaccam pakasentam, ","tha-ap537:3.2":"bodhayantam sadevakam; ","tha-ap537:3.3":"Vicittakathikanaggam, ","tha-ap537:3.4":"vannayantam mahajane. ","tha-ap537:4.1":"Tada muditacittoham, ","tha-ap537:4.2":"nimantetva tathagatam; ","tha-ap537:4.3":"Nanarattehi vatthehi, ","tha-ap537:4.4":"alankaritvana mandapam. ","tha-ap537:5.1":"Nanaratanapajjotam, ","tha-ap537:5.2":"sasangham bhojayim tahim; ","tha-ap537:5.3":"Bhojayitvana sattaham, ","tha-ap537:5.4":"nanaggarasabhojanam. ","tha-ap537:6.1":"Nanacittehi pupphehi, ","tha-ap537:6.2":"pujayitva sasavakam; ","tha-ap537:6.3":"Nipacca padamulamhi, ","tha-ap537:6.4":"tam thanam patthayim aham. ","tha-ap537:7.1":"Tada munivaro aha, ","tha-ap537:7.2":"karunekarasasayo; ","tha-ap537:7.3":"‘Passathetam dijavaram, ","tha-ap537:7.4":"padumananalocanam. ","tha-ap537:8.1":"Pitipamojjabahulam, ","tha-ap537:8.2":"samuggatatanuruham; ","tha-ap537:8.3":"Hasamhitavisalakkham, ","tha-ap537:8.4":"mama sasanalalasam. ","tha-ap537:9.1":"Patitam padamule me, ","tha-ap537:9.2":"ekavatthasumanasam; ","tha-ap537:9.3":"Esa pattheti tam thanam, ","tha-ap537:9.4":"vicittakathikattanam. ","tha-ap537:10.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap537:10.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap537:10.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap537:10.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap537:11.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap537:11.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap537:11.3":"Kumarakassapo nama, ","tha-ap537:11.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap537:12.1":"Vicittapupphadussanam, ","tha-ap537:12.2":"ratanananca vahasa; ","tha-ap537:12.3":"Vicittakathikanam so, ","tha-ap537:12.4":"aggatam papunissati’. ","tha-ap537:13.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap537:13.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap537:13.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap537:13.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap537:14.1":"Paribbhamam bhavabhave, ","tha-ap537:14.2":"rangamajjhe yatha nato; ","tha-ap537:14.3":"Sakhamigatrajo hutva, ","tha-ap537:14.4":"migiya kucchimokkamim. ","tha-ap537:15.1":"Tada mayi kucchigate, ","tha-ap537:15.2":"vajjhavaro upatthito; ","tha-ap537:15.3":"Sakhena catta me mata, ","tha-ap537:15.4":"nigrodham saranam gata. ","tha-ap537:16.1":"Tena sa migarajena, ","tha-ap537:16.2":"marana parimocita; ","tha-ap537:16.3":"Pariccajitva sapanam, ","tha-ap537:16.4":"mamevam ovadi tada. ","tha-ap537:17.1":"‘Nigrodhameva seveyya, ","tha-ap537:17.2":"na sakhamupasamvase; ","tha-ap537:17.3":"Nigrodhasmim matam seyyo, ","tha-ap537:17.4":"yance sakhamhi jivitam’. ","tha-ap537:18.1":"Tenanusittha migayuthapena, ","tha-ap537:18.2":"Ahanca mata ca tathetare ca; ","tha-ap537:18.3":"Agamma rammam tusitadhivasam, ","tha-ap537:18.4":"Gata pavasam sagharam yatheva. ","tha-ap537:19.1":"Puno kassapavirassa, ","tha-ap537:19.2":"atthamentamhi sasane; ","tha-ap537:19.3":"Aruyha selasikharam, ","tha-ap537:19.4":"yunjitva jinasasanam. ","tha-ap537:20.1":"Idanaham rajagahe, ","tha-ap537:20.2":"jato setthikule ahum; ","tha-ap537:20.3":"Apannasatta me mata, ","tha-ap537:20.4":"pabbaji anagariyam. ","tha-ap537:21.1":"Sagabbham tam viditvana, ","tha-ap537:21.2":"devadattamupanayum; ","tha-ap537:21.3":"So avoca ‘vinasetha, ","tha-ap537:21.4":"papikam bhikkhunim imam’. ","tha-ap537:22.1":"Idanipi munindena, ","tha-ap537:22.2":"jinena anukampita; ","tha-ap537:22.3":"Sukhini ajani mayham, ","tha-ap537:22.4":"mata bhikkhunupassaye. ","tha-ap537:23.1":"Tam viditva mahipalo, ","tha-ap537:23.2":"kosalo mam aposayi; ","tha-ap537:23.3":"Kumarapariharena, ","tha-ap537:23.4":"namenahanca kassapo. ","tha-ap537:24.1":"Mahakassapamagamma, ","tha-ap537:24.2":"aham kumarakassapo; ","tha-ap537:24.3":"Vammikasadisam kayam, ","tha-ap537:24.4":"sutva buddhena desitam. ","tha-ap537:25.1":"Tato cittam vimucci me, ","tha-ap537:25.2":"anupadaya sabbaso; ","tha-ap537:25.3":"Payasim damayitvaham, ","tha-ap537:25.4":"etadaggamapapunim. ","tha-ap537:26.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap537:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap537:26.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap537:27.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap537:27.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap537:27.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap537:28.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap537:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap537:28.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap537:29.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kumarakassapo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap537:30.1":"Kumarakassapattherassapadanam pancamam. ","tha-ap537:30.2":"Catuvisatimam bhanavaram. "}